<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>John Conway's Game of Life</title>
    <!-- 引入 Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- 引入 MathJax 用於渲染數學公式 -->
    <script src="https://polyfill.io/v3/polyfill.min.js?features=es6"></script>
    <script id="MathJax-script" async src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<!-- 移除了 justify-center 改用 py-10 讓長內容可以正常向下滾動 -->
<body class="flex flex-col items-center min-h-screen py-10 px-4 font-sans">

    <div class="max-w-4xl w-full flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
        
        <!-- 標題與遊戲區塊 -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2 text-green-400">John Conway's Game of Life</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base">點擊或拖曳網格繪製細胞，觀察它們的演化生命週期。</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 畫布容器 -->
        <div id="canvas-container" class="w-full aspect-video bg-black border-2 border-gray-700 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden relative">
            <canvas id="gameCanvas" class="w-full h-full cursor-crosshair"></canvas>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 控制面板 -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 w-full">
            <button id="startBtn" class="flex-1 min-w-[120px] bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-500 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg">
                開始 / 暫停
            </button>
            <button id="stepBtn" class="flex-1 min-w-[120px] bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg">
                單步執行
            </button>
            <button id="randomBtn" class="flex-1 min-w-[120px] bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg">
                隨機生成
            </button>
            <button id="clearBtn" class="flex-1 min-w-[120px] bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-500 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg">
                清除畫布
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- 速度設定區 (新增) -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex items-center gap-4 text-sm border border-gray-700">
            <label class="font-bold text-yellow-400 whitespace-nowrap">演化速度 (FPS):</label>
            <input type="range" id="speedSlider" min="1" max="60" value="15" class="flex-1 accent-yellow-500">
            <span id="speedVal" class="w-8 font-mono font-bold text-yellow-400 text-right">15</span>
        </div>

        <!-- 規則設定區 (拉桿) -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center text-sm border border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-3">
                <h3 class="text-blue-400 font-bold border-b border-gray-700 pb-1">存活條件 (活細胞保持存活的鄰居數)</h3>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <label class="w-12 text-right text-gray-300">最少:</label>
                    <input type="range" id="surviveMin" min="0" max="8" value="2" class="flex-1 accent-blue-500">
                    <span id="surviveMinVal" class="w-4 font-mono font-bold text-blue-400">2</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <label class="w-12 text-right text-gray-300">最多:</label>
                    <input type="range" id="surviveMax" min="0" max="8" value="3" class="flex-1 accent-blue-500">
                    <span id="surviveMaxVal" class="w-4 font-mono font-bold text-blue-400">3</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-3">
                <h3 class="text-green-400 font-bold border-b border-gray-700 pb-1">繁殖條件 (死細胞變為活細胞的鄰居數)</h3>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <label class="w-12 text-right text-gray-300">最少:</label>
                    <input type="range" id="reproduceMin" min="0" max="8" value="3" class="flex-1 accent-green-500">
                    <span id="reproduceMinVal" class="w-4 font-mono font-bold text-green-400">3</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <label class="w-12 text-right text-gray-300">最多:</label>
                    <input type="range" id="reproduceMax" min="0" max="8" value="3" class="flex-1 accent-green-500">
                    <span id="reproduceMaxVal" class="w-4 font-mono font-bold text-green-400">3</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 分隔線 -->
        <hr class="w-full border-gray-700 my-8">

        <!-- 理論與數學內涵區塊 (深色模式適配) -->
        <article class="w-full bg-gray-800/50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-700 text-left">
            
            <header class="mb-12 border-b border-gray-700 pb-6">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">
                    理論與數學內涵
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    康威生命遊戲並非傳統意義上具有「玩家」與「勝負」的遊戲，而是一種<strong>細胞自動機（Cellular Automaton）</strong>。其魅力在於透過極其簡單的規則，推演出極其複雜、甚至具備運算能力的動態系統。
                </p>
            </header>
            
            <!-- 1. 核心規則 -->
            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                    <span class="bg-indigo-900 text-indigo-300 w-8 h-8 rounded-full inline-flex justify-center items-center mr-3 text-sm">1</span>
                    核心規則：生存與毀滅
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4 text-gray-300">系統的演化是離散的（分步進行），每一代（Generation）的狀態完全取決於前一代。在您上方的標準設定中，遵循以下四條簡單規則：</p>
                
                <ul class="space-y-4 mt-6 text-gray-300">
                    <li class="flex items-start bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400 mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 17h8m0 0V9m0 8l-8-8-4 4-6-6"></path></svg>
                        <div><strong class="text-white">人口過少（Underpopulation）：</strong>若一個活細胞周圍的活鄰居少於 2 個，該細胞在下一代死亡（模擬孤單）。</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                        <div><strong class="text-white">穩定存續（Survival）：</strong>若一個活細胞周圍有 2 或 3 個活鄰居，該細胞在下一代繼續存活。</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400 mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path></svg>
                        <div><strong class="text-white">人口過剩（Overpopulation）：</strong>若一個活細胞周圍有超過 3 個活鄰居，該細胞在下一代死亡（模擬資源匱乏）。</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"></path></svg>
                        <div><strong class="text-white">繁殖（Reproduction）：</strong>若一個死細胞周圍正好有 3 個活鄰居，該細胞在下一代變為活細胞。</div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-400">
                    <strong>註：</strong> 這裡的「鄰居」是指 <strong>摩爾鄰域（Moore Neighborhood）</strong>，即一個細胞周圍相鄰的 8 個方格（上、下、左、右及四個對角線）。
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 2. 數學定義與內涵 -->
            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                    <span class="bg-indigo-900 text-indigo-300 w-8 h-8 rounded-full inline-flex justify-center items-center mr-3 text-sm">2</span>
                    數學定義與內涵
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-6 text-gray-300">生命遊戲在數學與理論計算機科學領域具有極高的研究價值，主要體現在以下幾個層面：</p>

                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">狀態函數與轉換</h3>
                        <p class="mb-3 text-gray-300">若令 \(S_{t}(i, j) \in \{0, 1\}\) 表示在時間 \(t\) 時，座標為 \((i, j)\) 的細胞狀態（1 為活，0 為死），則其演化可以表示為一個離散函數：</p>
                        <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 py-4 px-6 rounded-lg text-center overflow-x-auto shadow-inner text-white">
                            \[ S_{t+1}(i, j) = f(S_t(i, j), N_t(i, j)) \]
                        </div>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-300">其中 \(N_t(i, j)\) 是該細胞周圍 8 個鄰居的活細胞總和。</p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">圖靈完備性（Turing Completeness）</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300">這是生命遊戲最震撼的數學內涵。康威與後來的研究者證明，生命遊戲是<strong>圖靈完備</strong>的。這意味著：</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-2 text-gray-300 pl-2">
                            <li>可以在生命遊戲中構造出邏輯閘（AND, OR, NOT）。</li>
                            <li>可以利用特定的模式（如滑翔機槍 Glider Gun）來傳輸訊號。</li>
                            <li>理論上，只要初始盤面夠大，生命遊戲可以模擬任何通用計算機。</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 3. 典型的模式分類 -->
            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                    <span class="bg-indigo-900 text-indigo-300 w-8 h-8 rounded-full inline-flex justify-center items-center mr-3 text-sm">3</span>
                    典型的模式分類
                </h2>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <!-- 靜止狀態 -->
                    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-white">靜止狀態<br><span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-normal">Still Lifes</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-6 flex-grow">圖案在每一代都保持不變。例如：方塊 (Block)。</p>
                        <div class="flex justify-center">
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-1 bg-gray-900 p-2 rounded border border-gray-700">
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 振盪器 -->
                    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-white">振盪器<br><span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-normal">Oscillators</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-6 flex-grow">圖案在有限步數內循環回到初始狀態。例如：訊號燈 (Blinker)。</p>
                         <div class="flex justify-center items-center h-16">
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-1 bg-gray-900 p-2 rounded border border-gray-700">
                                <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-green-400 rounded-sm animate-pulse"></div>
                                <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-green-400 rounded-sm animate-pulse"></div>
                                <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-green-400 rounded-sm animate-pulse"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 移動圖樣 -->
                    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-white">移動圖樣<br><span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-normal">Spaceships</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-6 flex-grow">圖案在演化的過程中，位置會發生整體偏移。例如：滑翔機 (Glider)。</p>
                        <div class="flex justify-center h-16">
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-1 p-1 bg-gray-900 rounded border border-gray-700">
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-green-400 rounded-sm"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 4. 計算不可判定性 & 哲學意義 -->
            <section class="space-y-12">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                        <span class="bg-indigo-900 text-indigo-300 w-8 h-8 rounded-full inline-flex justify-center items-center mr-3 text-sm">4</span>
                        計算不可判定性 (Undecidability)
                    </h2>
                    <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-indigo-500 bg-indigo-900/30 p-4 rounded-r-lg text-gray-300 italic mb-4">
                        "不存在一個通用的演算法，能夠在給定任意初始配置的情況下，預知該系統最終是否會進入穩定狀態、週期循環，還是會無限擴張。"
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">要得知結果，唯一的辦法就是讓它「跑跑看」。這深刻地反映了數學中的決定論系統，同樣可以產生完全不可預知的長期結果。</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                        <span class="bg-indigo-900 text-indigo-300 w-8 h-8 rounded-full inline-flex justify-center items-center mr-3 text-sm">5</span>
                        哲學意義：自組織系統
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-300">生命遊戲清晰地展示了生命（或複雜的秩序）是如何從無序且極其簡單的底層規則中「自組織」形成的。</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">這也引發了關於「數位物理學」的深遠討論：如果簡單的 4 條規則就能產生如此複雜的宇宙，甚至在其中誕生能進行運算的實體，那麼我們現實世界的物理定律，是否本質上也只是某種更高級的細胞自動機規則呢？</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </article>

    </div>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>